title: Prana Health Food and Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Juice bar, Take-out
description: Deli and market. This small health food store is located in a strip-mall on 36th Street, just east of 826, and offers natural juices and a daily buffet for $10 featuring a variety of vegetarian hot and cold foods, such as lasagna, yuca, quinoa, tofu scramble, lentil soup, a mixed green salad, and other vegetarian items. Stocks books, incense, and products for sale.
